{
  "stem": "11611.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, although my original notion, as I told you, was to go there and do a reasonable amount of work, and coast, and see Europe, I wound up working, I would say, an average of 60 to 80 hours a week, which is more than I've ever done in private practice, although I had times when I averaged 60.",
      "word_count": 59
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in fact, from time to time, during the winter of '47, and in the winter of '48, I remember sleeping on the stone floors of the courthouse office that I had at Nuremberg.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had interpreters I had primarily Otto Werber.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was extremely good.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I'll get into it later, history or subsequently.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, he was as good as any of the staff people, the administrative people.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I also did a lot of traveling.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I spent a lot of time in Prague on business because the Dresdner Bank had taken over a very large chain of Czech banks, one of the largest, the [NON-ENGLISH] banks.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they've been active in the Sudeten territories, which the Germans took over.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I had lots of business trips to Prague, and I got to like it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Prague was only four hours by car from Nuremberg, reasonably-- Nuremberg's reasonably close to the Czech border.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Communist party.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was a communist government by February '48.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, there were two phases in Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Up till February '48, the government-- I'm trying to remember who the key Czech official was, Masaryk.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think his son was active-- committed suicide, allegedly, or was thrown out of a window in a very popular Eastern European sport called defenestration.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When I first went to Prague, it was a flourishing city and a hell of a lot nicer than it is today.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It wasn't damaged during the war.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
